            <title><![CDATA[Donut Inertness]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[
          <img style="display: none" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dnpmdb8r8/image/upload/argyleink/inert-donut.png" alt="some title" height="1024" width="1024" />
        <p>Just as <a href="https://developer.chrome.com/docs/css-ui/at-scope"><code>@scope</code></a> brought selector <a href="https://www.stubbornella.org/2011/10/08/scope-donuts/">donut scoping</a> to CSS (thanks <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/nicolesullivan.bsky.social">Nicole</a>!), so does <a href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/10711"><code>interactivity: inert;</code></a> bring <strong>donut inertness</strong>.</p>
<p><a href="https://codepen.io/argyleink/pen/YzmJXvP">Try it on Codepen</a> 🤘🏻💀<br>
<small>use <a href="https://www.google.com/chrome/canary/">Canary</a> with <a href="chrome://flags/#enable-experimental-web-platform-features">web experiments enabled</a></small></p>
]]></description>
